column5: The winner is ....  Robert Blowes (memart)  Give me a pm Robert to arrange collecting your prize.  Thanks for supporting Big Jim.  Congrats...  Matt
Hey bro WTG. What we win.

2 full days on the Ottawa river fishing muskies, 19.5 ' fully rigged muskie boat , all tackle supplied (unless you want to bring muskie gear), on board lunch, non Alcoholic drinks (those are for after). Pictures of your outing. 1 night accomodation at a local dump  ....and if all goes right ...some great big fish memories.  Just get to Ottawa!!  Guaranteed to be a good time!  M.
Who in thier right mind would turn down an invite to that. Thanks Bro.
Thanks Matt i look forward to it this is something i always wanted to try i will send you a pm  Rob
Way to go me brudder's brudder! I jess KNOW you'll have a great time!
no..Misfish needs to get out small mouth bass fishing he ain't got no time for muskie   so if there is an opening I am willing to go...LOL
Awesome Rob...can't wait to get you out on the mighty  "O" ....
